<p>Macroeconomics revision:</p>

<p>Statement in quotes usually has multiple interpretations
Have signposts at the start or end of the paragraph to show where youâ€™re leading
Simple and Direct English
Learn efficient definitions: Pareto efficiency, Subgame Equilibria
Everything in your essay should make a real contribution
Summarise the assumptions and results (Do not confuse assumptions and simplifying assumptions)Â 
When multiple models, discuss one/two in detail and then briefly compare with the other models</p>

<p>Example: Insurance Question:
Simple Model, Assumptions: Two types, competitive insurance (zero profits), risk neutral insurance,Â risk averse individuals</p>

